{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/shorthand-property-no-redundant-values/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/unit-blacklist/","description":"unit-whitelist 指定允许的单位的白名单。 选项 array|string: \\[\"array\", \"of\", \"units\"]|\"unit\" 给定： 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规： 可选的辅助选项 ignoreProperties: { unit:…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"unit-whitelist\"><a href=\"#unit-whitelist\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>unit-whitelist</h1>\n<p>指定允许的单位的白名单。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100px</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**           ↑\n *  这个单位 */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>array|string</code>: <code>[\"array\", \"of\", \"units\"]|\"unit\"</code></p>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"px\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"em\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"deg\"</span>]</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10rem</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">animation</span>: animation-name <span class=\"hljs-number\">5s</span> ease; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-size</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.2em</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">line-height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.2</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100PX</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rotate</span>(30deg); }</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"可选的辅助选项\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%89%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>可选的辅助选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"ignoreproperties--unit-property-regex-regex-\"><a href=\"#ignoreproperties--unit-property-regex-regex-\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>ignoreProperties: { unit: [\"property\", \"/regex/\", /regex/] }</code></h3>\n<p>忽略指定属性的声明中值的单位。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>[\"px\", \"em\"]</code>。</p>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"rem\"</span>: [ <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"line-height\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/^border/\"</span> ],\n  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"%\"</span>: [ <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"width\"</span> ]\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">line-height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.1rem</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-bottom-width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">6rem</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">20rem</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">-moz-border-radius-topright</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20rem</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/unit-whitelist.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/unit-whitelist/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/unit-whitelist/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/unit-whitelist/index.html.596aa9175c47e7e33e841ce36ea1c832.json"}